  lines:
  - Hello, Traveller I am the mayor of this town and we need your help!
  - There's a monster trying to get through the portal to destroy our town!
  - We need you to destroy all the monster and saves us!
  - The portal is on your right take it! and destroy all of them!
  - Please return safely and good luck Traveller!
